.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-LIST-EXPIRED" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-list-expired \- list expired invoices, newest first
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-list-expired
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns expired invoices sorted by expiry time descending.
Default limit is 50.
Returns an empty array if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{label, payment_hash, amount_msat, expires_at}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-list (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-list-paid (1)
